data.text: Angʼo momiyo isedagiwa nyaka chiengʼ, yaye Nyasaye?
Par jogi mane ingʼiewo chon gi lala,
Lokri ichom kuonde mosebedo kokethore nyaka nene,
Wasiki noruto kama iromoe kodwa;
Negitimore marach mana ka ji mangʼawo leyegi malo
Negituro chumbe modol odol
Ne giwangʼo kari maler mar lemo molokore buru,
Negiwacho e chunygi niya, “Wabiro tiekogi chuth!”
Tinde ok wayud honni kata ranyisi,
Nyaka karangʼo ma jasigu biro jarie, yaye Nyasaye?
Angʼo momiyo itamo lweti tiyo tichne,
To Nyasaye in e Ruodha nyaka chakre chon, yaye Nyasaye,
In ema ne ipogo nam e diere ariyo gi tekoni,
In ema ne itoyo wiye Leviathan,
In ema ne iyawo sokni gi aore,
Odiechiengʼ en mari, kendo otieno bende mari,
In ema ne iketo tongʼ duto mag piny
Parie kaka jasigu osejari, yaye Jehova Nyasaye.
Kik iyie ichiw ngima mar akuch oduglani ne le mager mag bungu;
Par singruok mari
Kik iyie mondo joma idiyo ringa ka wigi okuot,
Aa malo mondo isir tichni, yaye Nyasaye;
Kik wiyi wil gi sibuoch wasiki,
